<p>Well I keep trying to find some kind of skill cap list for each class on here and I can't seem to find one so i'm going to post a request to allakhazam a few times, sorry for all the extra subjects in each class discussion forum... <br /> <br />I'm sure i'm not the only person that has noticed that casters realms information is outdated and inaccurate more often than not, there skill cap lists do not include the new expansions from what i have seen, for that matter they don't even show information on the new berserker class at all.&nbsp;&nbsp;I think it would be a very good addition to Allakhazam to put in a list of skill caps by class and level along with starting stat information and what new skills are available at what levels.  Casters realm does have a very nice section for this, but as i mentioned they are outdated and innacurate on alot of things so one never knows if they can trust the information there.  Please help alla!!</p>
